name: Theresa's Swimsuit 泳裝德麗莎 | Honkai Impact 3rd
description:
.

morning_sunshine_v1-044 contains only one suit "morning sunshine"

shallow_sunset_v4-025 contains only one suit "shallow sunset"

These two don't need to write tag "blue_eyes" and "white_hair"

.

v4 contains two swimsuits for Theresa Apocalypse from Honkai Impact 3rd

v4 包含崩壞三德麗莎的兩套泳裝

.

Morning Sunshine（初升晨日）:

(masterpiece:1.2), (best quality:1.3), morning_sunshine, 1girl, blue_eyes, white_hair, swimsuit, pink frilled_bikini, bikini_skirt

.

Shallow Sunset（落日淺岸）:

(masterpiece:1.2), (best quality:1.3), shallow_sunset, 1girl, blue_eyes, white_hair, straw_hat, swimsuit, dress, shorts, flower, starfish

.

The second one works better than the first one

第二套生出來的圖比較好一點

.

Although only the second suit has a straw hat in the design, sometimes it appers too when generating the first one. I think it is fine, but you can add it to negative prompt if you don't want it.

雖然在原設計中只有第二套有戴草帽，但在生成第一套的圖片時，有時候也會出現。我是覺得ok，如果你不想要的話就寫在negative prompt裡面吧

.

德麗莎世界第一可愛！

兩套服裝我都沒有，而且不知道有沒有復刻可能（悲

下次應該會上傳觀星的

.
